{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The horror game <i>Bordermind: Thoughts and Visions Beyond the Limits</i> is a retro first-person shooter with classic features typical of games in this genre.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro full 3D, 2000s visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tutorial.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satisfying shooting sequences, sniper sequences, jumpscares, and creepiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After the death of your wife, a lot has changed in you, and the way you've dealt with it may not have been the best.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You understand that you need to speak to her again, so you seek out a device used in World War II to contact the dead\u00a0and enter an intermediary world between the material and the spiritual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll have to face what comes from the dark, deal with the remnants of soldiers, confront your own fears, and find a way to delve even deeper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735867179","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324130/page.bg.jpg?t=1735867179","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324130/f9ae4bc5cf9d73b84764dc09519011a74039cd9c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735867179","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324130/f9ae4bc5cf9d73b84764dc09519011a74039cd9c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735867179","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Frights, darkness, gore, killing undead people, undead cultists, monsters, mutants, intense shooti